message:
I can't reproduce the dead lock in Asp.Net using your sample. Is it always hang? How should i test it to see the problem? I have defined a helper GetJsonAsync(string uri) method as:

return await client.GetStringAsync(uri); 

and call it inside my controller as:

  var jsonTask = MyHelper.GetJsonAsync("https://reqres.in/api/users/3");
  return jsonTask.Result.ToString();

But no dead lock happens. it simply return the desired sample data from the api without any problem. Whats wrong here?
